Package: meridianR
Title: R Interface to Google Meridian (Marketing Mix Modeling)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ben Denis", "Shaffer", , "shafferbendenis@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R interface to Google's 'Meridian' Bayesian Marketing Mix
    Modeling (MMM) library. Wraps the 'Meridian' 'Python' package via
    'reticulate', providing faithful bindings to its data, model, and analysis
    objects together with an idiomatic R layer for loading data, configuring
    priors and model specifications, fitting models, and analyzing results.
